        %a{ :href => "http://facebook.com/Some1Else", :title => "Srđan Prodanović, Some1Else" }
          Srđan Prodanović
        in
        %a{ :href => "http://miha.rebernik.info/", :title => "Miha Rebernik, majx" }
          Miha Rebernik
        \.
      %p
        Rails je razvil
        %a{ :href => "http://www.loudthinking.com/about.html" }
          David Heinemeier Hansson
        , nadgrajujejo pa ga člani
        %a{ :href => "http://groups.google.com/group/rubyonrails-core" }
          Rails core
        skupine.

